Download rtaudio-4.0.6.tar.gz from rtaudio distribution. 
Uncompress rtaudio-4.0.6.tar.gz into current directory, so it will be located in rtaudio-4.0.6 subdirectory and run "make PCMHOST=rtaudio" from interfaces/pcm directory of sid.

To build, type command:
make

build options: 
	TARGET_ARCH=(default i686, see ../../buildfiles/arch directory for other TARGET_ARCH options) - build for specific architecture
	verbose=(0 | 1, default 0) - be verbose

To clean build, type:
make clean
